      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/3adb348a-bea8-11e0-8bdf-52540025f9af).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
